actually happened--

00:53:18.579 --> 00:53:20.370
and there are still
people working on this.

00:53:20.370 --> 00:53:23.930
There are people--
just bear with me here

00:53:23.930 --> 00:53:27.090
as I find t he right slide.

00:53:27.090 --> 00:53:31.590
Let's be clear that wireless
power works in certain ways.

00:53:31.590 --> 00:53:36.340
So, for example,
through the 1990s,

00:53:36.340 --> 00:53:41.200
the US Navy used extremely
low-frequency radio waves

00:53:41.200 --> 00:53:43.560
that could travel
through what's called

00:53:43.560 --> 00:53:46.690
the Schumann cavity,
which is the cavity that

00:53:46.690 --> 00:53:51.080
