the way that the navy

00:54:21.510 --> 00:54:23.470
kept in touch with the subs.

00:54:23.470 --> 00:54:27.190
So you can send radio
waves, you can send energy,

00:54:27.190 --> 00:54:30.940
through the earth, and
that's what this illustrates.

00:54:30.940 --> 00:54:33.420
A company that's
actually got roots here

00:54:33.420 --> 00:54:38.830
in Cambridge and at MIT
